Hurry up!

00:28:47.240 --> 00:28:47.840
Finished.

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:48.400
Out.

00:28:48.430 --> 00:28:49.440
Pass.

00:28:50.680 --> 00:28:51.610
I'll match five.

00:28:53.640 --> 00:28:54.050
Five, right?

00:28:54.050 --> 00:28:54.400
Still calling?

00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:55.030
Ten.

00:28:55.750 --> 00:28:56.610
Show the cards.

00:28:57.350 --> 00:28:57.980
Cao Xiaojun.

