My turn.

00:28:58.720 --> 00:28:59.580
Come play a few rounds.

00:28:59.580 --> 00:29:00.840
Help me change my luck.

00:29:01.110 --> 00:29:02.070
No money.

00:29:03.590 --> 00:29:04.750
That's no fun.

00:29:04.790 --> 00:29:05.680
Every time I ask you to play,

00:29:05.680 --> 00:29:06.550
you're broke.

00:29:06.600 --> 00:29:07.110
If you don't play,

00:29:07.110 --> 00:29:08.840
how will you know if you can win?

00:29:09.070 --> 00:29:09.680
Go ahead and play.

00:29:09.680 --> 00:29:10.480
You guys play.

00:29:12.510 --> 00:29:13.590
Hey, guy on the top bunk,

00:29:13.590 --> 00:29:15.160
come down and play
Three-Card Brag.

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:15.690
This game

00:29:15.720 --> 00:29:16.880
is only fun with more people.

