00:29:50.720 --> 00:29:51.270
I'm talking to you.

00:29:51.270 --> 00:29:52.310
Go buy some beer.

00:29:54.030 --> 00:29:55.070
You asking for trouble?

00:29:55.070 --> 00:29:55.730
Stop, stop.

00:29:57.480 --> 00:29:58.790
Cheng. Cheng.

00:29:59.480 --> 00:30:00.070
Don't stoop to his level.

00:30:00.070 --> 00:30:00.870
Ni Xiangdong,

00:30:01.070 --> 00:30:01.750
let's go.

00:30:02.350 --> 00:30:03.280
I'll go with you.

00:30:06.370 --> 00:30:07.310
That bastard Wang Cheng

00:30:07.310 --> 00:30:08.910
just likes causing trouble.

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:10.720
