Nothing we can do.

00:30:24.480 --> 00:30:26.140
Just avoid him when possible.

00:30:26.240 --> 00:30:27.750
He's just a bully

00:30:27.830 --> 00:30:29.690
because his uncle is the foreman.

00:30:30.340 --> 00:30:31.440
On his own merit,

00:30:31.830 --> 00:30:32.790
he's nothing.

00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:40.480
My taking leave today

00:30:41.640 --> 00:30:44.240
will just give him
another excuse to harass me.

