You've never had
pork stewed with vermicelli?

00:32:10.700 --> 00:32:11.260
No.

00:32:12.030 --> 00:32:13.750
Come back to the Northeast
with me and try that.

00:32:13.750 --> 00:32:15.240
I'll treat you to
pork stewed with vermicelli

00:32:15.240 --> 00:32:17.100
and pig-slaughter feast dishes.

00:32:17.830 --> 00:32:18.640
Sure.

00:32:19.350 --> 00:32:21.350
If I get a chance to visit Northeast.

00:32:22.440 --> 00:32:23.270
I still need

00:32:23.350 --> 00:32:24.350
to work here.

