I'm quitting.

00:32:37.070 --> 00:32:38.000
Not coming back?

00:32:38.720 --> 00:32:39.920
It's not profitable.

00:32:40.070 --> 00:32:42.270
Look, there's nobody even at mealtime.

00:32:46.640 --> 00:32:47.900
So I'm going back home.

